Primary, I focus on my cognative functions and how this affects my perception and processing of reality and external stimulus. In addition to congative processes, I have found that there are many personality assessment that assist me in accurately determining certain tendencies and responses that I have in regards to things like expectations, friends, authority and making decisions.
